record.title: REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H. RES. 618
record.narrative:
REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H. RES. 618 -- (House of Representatives - October 10, 2007)

[Page: H11464]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent to remove my name as a cosponsor of H. Res. 618.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentlewoman from New York?
